{"tid":33595,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"華為成功研發石墨烯電池","createTime":"2016-12-11T02:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T04:55:29.000Z","uid":50856,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"903cdb5b9c94b0572daf6224ac97391dcf1634c6","tid":33595,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:09:07.000Z","msg":"近年各地科技家都在研究不同的物料來發展新電池技術，而在新電池物料中以石墨烯為現時最成熟的新物料。華為中央研究院瓦特實驗室日前剛發布首款高溫、長壽的石墨烯基鋰離子電池，月內就會發布超級快速充電手機。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n加入石墨烯的鋰子電池的工作溫度上限可以再提高多10℃，電池可承受溫度提高，代表可以充入的電壓電流更大，達至快速充電的效果。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n去年華為實驗室就測試過5分鐘就可以把3000mAh的電池充滿48%，可以解決現時手機充電慢耗電快的問題。而且新電池比一般鋰電長壽兩倍。石墨烯電池可以應用在通訊基站的UPS、電動車以及無人機等電耗大的產品上。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n官方表示，本月底就會發布一款以快充為賣點的快充手機。&nbsp;"},{"pid":"800535f68efce421eedf9fd8e477aa370cce6aed","tid":33595,"uid":25189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808943e6c36f36e1e6f0869aec7e9b837b1a5fc8","tid":33595,"uid":4324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"華為可信都大， 小米既就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e200e001c0b21f1026c7d367fe0ba0f63e3ee4","tid":33595,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:57:27.000Z","msg":"五毛後進化成百萬後?"},{"pid":"aac9b7a934b7fa02bb628a83fcf58aa571c71573","tid":33595,"uid":23964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"炸撚死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fdf3f013bf9442e61b2199baa131146c8c7a7e","tid":33595,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:29:06.00